Einstein Bot Blocks

Bot blocks let you add prebuilt functionality to your bot without cloning a bot or building a new one. Create a bot block to add a dialog group to multiple bots. or import a block from the Einstein Bots library.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Import an Einstein Bot Block
Bot blocks are a group of components that you can import to multiple bots. Blocks are pieces of bots, as opposed to a bot template, which contains functionality for a whole bot.

Create an Einstein Bot Block
Create an Einstein bot block to share specific functions inside your bot with other bots. You can package bot templates and share them between orgs or on AppExchange.

Explore the Einstein Bot Block Library
Learn about Einstein bot blocks designed for specific clouds and use cases.
